reviewText: One of the more innovative "buddy" movies, imo, combining a neat caper drama with hilarious comedic bits (a la "Odd Couple" sort of stuff). Definitely worth a watch.
It's a movie. I would't have bought it if I didn't enjoy it.
Excellent plot; between the players; fast moving; dialog superb; a fun movie to watchj
One of my favorite movies! Billy Bob and Bruce Willis work great together in this great film. You'll laugh and you may cry. A must have.
